 From going up Table Mountain to enjoying a game of pool and playing pranks on hotel guests Bieber is in his element.Bieber was spotted in the line to go up Table Mountain on Tuesday. It s reported he asked people not to take pictures but did happily chat to people who recognised him.On Wednesday night he reportedly aired a live Instagram video of himself playing pranks on guests at the One &amp; Only. He was also seen during the day trying to get a tan.